Sentencas: Cathode material BaBi0.05CO0.8Ta0.15 O3-delta (BBCT) was synthesized by a solid-state reaction for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The X-ray techniques had been used for structural characterizations.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: BBCT forms a pure cubic perovskite structure and exhibits chemical compatibility with the La(0.9)Sr(0.1)G(0.8)Mg(0.2)O(3-delta__) (LSGM) electrolyte.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of the BBCT is 20 x 10(-6) K-1.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity are 7.4-10.7 S cm(-1) in the temperature range of 600-800 degrees C in ambient air.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization resistance (Rp) of BBCT cathode on LSGM electrolyte is 0.023, 0.036, 0.065 Omega cm(2) at 800, 750, 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Maximum power density is 664 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The encouraging results promise BBCT as an alternative cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Novel BaBi0.05Co0.8Ta0.15O3-δ cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
